# ğŸ“ Student Dashboard API

## ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

The Student Dashboard API is a RESTful backend application built using Node.js and Express.js.  
It allows users to manage student records by performing CRUD operations and filtering students based on branch.

This API demonstrates proper routing, status code handling, and clean backend structure.

