## ğŸ’» Steps to Run Locally

1. Clone the repository

git clone https://github.com/amankumarb778-crypto/server-1.git

2. Navigate into project folder

cd server-1

3. Install dependencies

npm install

4. Start the server

node index.js

5. Open in browser or Postman

http://localhost:3000

